title: You Ain't Black (Joe Biden Interview and more)
itunes:title: You Ain't Black (Joe Biden Interview and more)
description:
Charlamagne had the opportunity to do a long overdue interview with former Vice President Joe Biden, where they spoke about the plans he has in turning around the economy, the 1994 crime bill and so much more. Also, we had actor and author Dondre Whitfield who spoke about his new book "Male vs. Man" and the difference between them and more. Moreover, Charlamagne gave an intoxicated person from his favorite place, Florida "Donkey of the Day" for getting mad at people that did not want to kiss and hug her
